33
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,940
<i>Okay, okay, I got it.</i>

34
00:01:56,940 --> 00:02:00,190
Anyway, it's just as well.
The sun's out.

35
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:02,410
Get a load of this.

36
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,980
Say cheeseburger!

37
00:02:07,820 --> 00:02:12,240
We can go up for a flight and do
aerial photography of Ponyland!

38
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,410
Terrific! Let's go!

39
00:02:14,410 --> 00:02:15,630
Danny, you be careful.

40
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:18,960
We'll be fine!

41
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,220
Let's just go straight.

42
00:02:22,220 --> 00:02:23,550
Sounds good to me.

43
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:29,180
That was straight?

44
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:31,650
Sure! But there's a
tail wind today.

45
00:02:31,650 --> 00:02:32,900
(laughs)

46
00:02:36,650 --> 00:02:38,520
Oh! This is so exciting.

47
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,980
