famous gizmonks in the world!

50
00:02:46,610 --> 00:02:48,660
Gock and Gluda the Great.

51
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:49,990
Inventors of the one and only

52
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:53,920
steam-powered, multi-tasking
double-ant whistle.

53
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:55,430
Tamers of the only

54
00:02:55,420 --> 00:02:58,330
lesser crested snicklewhacker
in the world!

55
00:02:58,340 --> 00:03:01,050
Inventors of gadgets and gizmos

56
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:04,170
and hyper super-duper
technical things.

57
00:03:04,180 --> 00:03:07,970
Some of which we don't
even know what they are, yet.

58
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:11,300
♪ But here is
the fun part ♪

59
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:14,300
♪ Inventing is such fun ♪

60
